PortSystem 1.0
PortGroup perl5 1.0

perl5.setup		Test-Harness 2.46
maintainers		darwin@opendarwin.org
description		Run perl standard test scripts with statistics.
long_description	You can write test scripts without knowing the exact \
				output this module expects by using "Test" modules. However, \
				by using this module, you can know the specifics, and you can \
				prints some performance statistics that are computed by the \
				Benchmark module.
homepage		http://search.cpan.org/~msergeant/${distname}/
